Blackheart smiled, "It seems Tyrael's troops can handel themselves...even if 
they had help from the maximals its an impressive victory none the less." He 
sent out a comm to the tripreds. "Fellow tripreds...I have come to help you 
whipe out this planet of foreign factions. We have won the war on cybertron. 
We are victorious. This is now the final battle and we shall win it! If you 
have any wounded just send the word and ill send a medical pod down and bring 
them up to the ship were they will be treated, we have spare cr's."

--part1_4f.26ebad52.2b0868d3_boundary
